---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import ScenePatternA from "../components/ScenePatternA.astro";
---
<PageLayout title="Per Gestori" description="Coordina la tua squadra di trader da un'unica infrastruttura operativa." locale="it">
  <section class="relative bg-blu text-paper min-h-screen flex items-center px-8 py-24" style="z-index: 10;">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] opacity-50 mb-6">Per chi coordina 5-20 trader</p>
      <h1 class="text-[clamp(28px,4.5vw,70px)] font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[0.95] mb-8 text-center">
        Coordina la tua squadra<br>di trader.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-80 max-w-2xl mb-12 font-medium">
        Vista aggregata su tutta la squadra. Movimenti e registri operativi tracciati per ogni ambiente. Senza fogli Excel sparsi.
      </p>
      <a href="#preventivo" class="inline-block px-9 py-4 bg-paper text-blu rounded-full font-bold hover:opacity-90">
        Richiedi preventivo →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ScenePatternA bgClass="bg-celeste" textClass="text-ink" wordsClass="text-ink/[0.04]" eyebrow="01 — multi-trader scoping" title="Ogni trader vede solo i suoi.<br>Tu vedi tutti." wordLeft="ogni" wordRight="suo" zIndex={11}>
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-ink text-paper flex items-center justify-center p-12">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium opacity-80 leading-relaxed">Multi-tenant con scoping per utente. Ogni trader vede solo i propri ambienti, i propri movimenti e i propri registri. Tu, da admin, hai una vista aggregata e filtrabile.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ScenePatternA>

  <ScenePatternA bgClass="bg-giallo" textClass="text-ink" wordsClass="text-ink/[0.04]" eyebrow="02 — stato operativo" title="Stato operativo chiaro.<br>Per ogni trader." wordLeft="stato" wordRight="chiaro" zIndex={12}>
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-ink text-paper flex items-center justify-center p-12">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium opacity-80 leading-relaxed">Eventi rilevati in tempo reale via WebSocket. Quando un ambiente broker chiude un'operazione, il sistema riallinea lo stato in 200–500ms. Niente disallineamenti da andare a inseguire.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ScenePatternA>

  <ScenePatternA bgClass="bg-viola" textClass="text-ink" wordsClass="text-ink/[0.05]" eyebrow="03 — registro integrato" title="Movimenti e registri<br>per ogni trader, per ogni ambiente." wordLeft="registro" wordRight="integrato" zIndex={13}>
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-surface text-ink border border-[color:var(--color-border)] flex items-center justify-center p-12">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium opacity-80 leading-relaxed">Movimenti tracciati, dossier annuale ordinato, niente Excel cross-trader. Esporti CSV pronto per il commercialista.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ScenePatternA>

  <ScenePatternA bgClass="bg-celeste-2" textClass="text-paper" wordsClass="text-paper/[0.06]" eyebrow="04 — multi-broker" title="Tradovate. MetaApi. ProjectX.<br>Tutti gli ambienti. Tutti i trader." wordLeft="ambienti" wordRight="collegati" zIndex={14}>
    <div class="w-full h-full bg-ink text-paper flex items-center justify-center p-12 border border-white/5">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-xl font-medium opacity-80 leading-relaxed">Una connessione provider per ogni trader, indipendente e isolata. Apex, FTMO, Topstep, Lucid, Tradeify — qualsiasi combinazione all'interno della squadra.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </ScenePatternA>

  <section id="preventivo" class="bg-paper px-8 py-24 relative" style="z-index: 25;">
    <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(20px,2.5vw,36px)] font-black tracking-[-0.04em] leading-[0.95] mb-4 text-center">
        Costruiamo insieme il tuo piano.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-center text-ink/60 mb-12 text-base font-medium">
        Compila in 2 minuti. Ti rispondiamo entro 24h con una proposta personalizzata in base al numero di trader e slot da coordinare.
      </p>

      <form
        action="https://formspree.io/f/REPLACE_ME"
        method="POST"
        class="space-y-5"
      >
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Nome e cognome *</label>
          <input type="text" name="name" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-ink/5 border-2 border-ink/10 rounded-xl focus:border-ink focus:outline-none font-medium" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Email *</label>
          <input type="email" name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-ink/5 border-2 border-ink/10 rounded-xl focus:border-ink focus:outline-none font-medium" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Numero di trader coordinati *</label>
          <select name="team_size" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-ink/5 border-2 border-ink/10 rounded-xl focus:border-ink focus:outline-none font-medium">
            <option value="">Seleziona...</option>
            <option value="1-5">1-5</option>
            <option value="6-10">6-10</option>
            <option value="11-20">11-20</option>
            <option value="20+">20+</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Prop firm utilizzate</label>
          <input type="text" name="prop_firms" placeholder="es. APEX, FTMO, Topstep..." class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-ink/5 border-2 border-ink/10 rounded-xl focus:border-ink focus:outline-none font-medium" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Messaggio (opzionale)</label>
          <textarea name="message" rows="4" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-ink/5 border-2 border-ink/10 rounded-xl focus:border-ink focus:outline-none font-medium"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="w-full px-9 py-4 bg-ink text-paper rounded-full font-bold hover:opacity-90">
          Invia richiesta →
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
